FIRST AID: Basic emergency medical treatment

Category: Medical
Base skill: 45% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

Palladium's baseline medical skill: stopping bleeding, treating shock,
and stabilizing a wounded patient using nothing more than bandages or
a basic medical kit. Most OCCs with any medical background start with
some level of First Aid; it does not require the surgical training
that Paramedic or Medical Doctor do.

Command: treat <target> / bandage <target>
  Requires bandages, a first aid kit, or a medkit in your inventory.
  Rolls your First Aid percentage; on success the target recovers 1d6
  SDC or HP. See "help bandage" for the full command syntax.

